# 2.0.0
- avatar is now on a separate layer from the desk, and on top of the arm, so the arm looks much better
- toggle debug view with CTRL-D
- removed distinction between mouse and tablet (achievable by skins)
- prepared file structure for skins
- filename changes
    - `cat.png` -> `avatar.png`
    - `mousebg.png` -> `background.png`
- config
    - removed entries relating to original hand drawing
    - `stretchyArm` key is no longer needed as there is no alternative

